South Africa Posts August Budget Deficit of 5.4 Billion Rand

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-09-30T12:16:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/south-africa-posts-august-budget-deficit-of-5-4-billion-rand.html
South Africa  posted a budget
deficit of 5.4 billion rand in August, the National Treasury
said.  Government revenue was 62.3 billion rand last month, while
expenditure reached 67.7 billion rand, the Pretoria-based
Treasury said in a statement on its website today.  The budget deficit for the first five months of the year
widened to 86.8 billion rand from 78.2 billion rand in the same
period a year ago, according to the statement  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  